                                        "value": "The coolness breaks when one of them asks, \"What if I bomb the Wisdom section and didn't do the other two?\" Everyone turns to me, suddenly less confident. \"Well,\" I say, \"my plan is to look at the steepest section first. That's the Wisdom section. If you don't attempt it, or if you fail to meet the success criteria of the rubric, then I'll evaluate the next-steepest section. That would be the Understanding section. If you're successful there, then you'll earn a ",
