                                        "nodeType": "text",
                                        "value": "Capital points (CPs) are the currency of CIVGAME. Every decision a team makes requires an expenditure of capital. Transporting troops, fighting wars, establishing colonies, buying resources, building health systemsâ€”all of it costs. A state earns most of its CPs through team averages on summative assessments: 40 CPs for a good-try ",
